idy. And <strong>you can only apply for one subsidy per calendar year</strong>. Consequently, a truck/tractor is only eligible <strong>in 1 calendar year</strong>. Vehicles previously declared in an aided application are therefore no longer eligible for aid in a subsequent application, including any new owner or leaseholder).</li></ul><h3>Deadline</h3><ul><li>Applications for 2023 can be submitted as long as there is budget and no later than <strong>30 November 2023</strong>. From 2024, the support measure will not be continued.</li></ul><h3>Follow-up</h3><ul><li>Once the application has been correctly submitted, the company will receive an <strong>acknowledgement of receipt</strong> at the e-mail address provided.</li><li>If the application file progresses normally, the company will receive <strong>an e-mail within 2 months with the decision</strong> and, in case of approval, the notification that the payment order for the requested subsidy has been issued.</li></ul>",
